snippet.title: RWBY: Grimm Eclipse - Nora Valkyrie from JNPR gameplay
snippet.description:
Just gameplay video to show Nora Valkyrie character from JNPR team.
Starting from beginning ("Boots on the Ground" level) with 2nd level character on Eclipse difficulty. 2nd level here because i'm already tried to record this video 2 times before, but get 2 fail attempts (first one with HDD empty space limit, second with electricity power cutoff because weather xD ). Sorry for my English.
